item.title: Cross-Country OCC Hookup
item.description: Three of the Irish OpenCoffees are on at the same time tomorrow (Limerick, Waterford and Dublin). They are doing some live video hookups along with live blogging/tweeting/jaikuing. Sounds like it’ll be a lot of fun! All the details over at Brightspark Blog.
